This directory contains the source code for Chapter 10.

This contains the following files:

- MemoryMapReadOnly.java - This is the memory-mapped example shown in Figure 10.21

- vfork.c - An example program illustrating vfork() - the virtual-memory fork.

- read-vs-mmap.pdf - A paper from Sun Microsystems illustrating the performance benefits
of memory-mapping a file.
This paper uses an example of scaling an image and compares the performance of
of scaling the image using memory-mapping and traditional read-writeI/O.
